metadata.title: Food Habits Database
metadata.description: Contains stomach content information of selected commercial Bering Sea species. Data included location parameters, stomach content descriptions, intestinal content information, and length of prey items.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: Determine feeding habits and consumption rates of commercially important species.

Status: In Progress

Maintenance frequency: Annually

Access constraints: Read only
